&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;We are looking for a Band 7 Ward Sister /Charge Nurse for our acute medical unit (AMU).&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note this post is for Wye Valley NHS Trust employees only.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role of the ward sister / charge nurse is to provide clinical and managerial leadership to the nursing and multi-disciplinary team. You will be required to be fully engaged with the other departments on the acute floor and working on AMU is vibrant and fast paced.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be leading ateam to deliver high standards of care. We are a dedicated, professional, and friendly team and are looking for an experienced nurse leader to join us. We are committed to teaching and supporting staff and are looking for these qualities in a new team member.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A strong clinical background is required with proven leadership experience essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
